data.title: 663 graduate from MSU Texas in Spring 2023
data.meta_description: Midwestern State University had 663 undergraduate and graduate students who were candidates for degrees in May 2023 with the provision that they meet all requirements as prescribed by the faculty and administration. Honor graduates receiving bachelor degrees included 68 summa cum laude, 90 magna cum laude, and 83 cum laude. Honor requirements are a grade point average of 3.9-4.0 for summa cum laude, 3.7-3.89 for magna cum laude, and 3.5-3.69 for cum laude. Honor graduates are designated in the list below.
data.text:
Midwestern State University had 663 undergraduate and graduate students who were candidates for degrees in May 2023 with the provision that they meet all requirements as prescribed by the faculty and administration. Honor graduates receiving bachelor degrees included 68 summa cum laude, 90 magna cum laude, and 83 cum laude. Honor requirements are a grade point average of 3.9-4.0 for summa cum laude, 3.7-3.89 for magna cum laude, and 3.5-3.69 for cum laude. Honor graduates are designated in the list below.
